Sheet: 04-USB-Storage-Interface.kicad_sch
Scope: USB host connector path for storage, VBUS power switch/protection, ESD and filtering.
Inputs: USB_HOST_D+, USB_HOST_D-, +5V_USB, GND
Outputs: USB_VBUS_SW, USB_OC# (optional)
Symbols/Footprints: USB connector, TVS/ESD array, ferrite bead, power switch (if used).
